    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Ready for a dependable, well-maintained ride that delivers real value? This vehicle is in good condition \u2014 it drives smoothly, the major systems are in solid working order, and it presents well inside and out. It's not brand new, but it's been cared for and shows it. Whether you're commuting daily or hitting the open road, this is a trustworthy choice at a fair price. Come take it for a spin \u2014 we think you'll be impressed!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "Pristine and picture-perfect \u2014 this is the one you've been waiting for! This vehicle is in absolutely mint condition, boasting a flawless, unmarked interior and an exterior that turns heads with zero visible blemishes. Every system runs smoothly, and the attention to care this car has received is evident the moment you lay eyes on it. Whether you're a discerning daily driver or a collector seeking a top-tier example, this car delivers the real deal. Come see it in person \u2014 we're confident it will exceed your expectations!",
      "price": 48000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Honest Deal for the Right Buyer \u2014 Priced to Move! \ud83d\udd27 This vehicle is in poor condition, and we're being upfront about it! It does run, which is a great starting point, but it will need some meaningful work to get it performing at its best. The exterior and interior show clear signs of wear, so come in with realistic expectations. If you're a hands-on buyer, a DIY mechanic, or someone looking for an affordable project, this could be a fantastic opportunity! Priced fairly at $5,000 to reflect its current state \u2014 a straightforward deal with no surprises. \ud83d\udee0\ufe0f",
      "price": 5000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly in poor condition \u2014 buyers should understand upfront that this car has significant issues and is priced to reflect that reality. The exterior shows substantial wear, including visible rust spots, dents, and faded or peeling paint in multiple areas. The interior has seen better days, with torn or heavily worn upholstery, cracked dashboard components, and general neglect throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the car has known issues that will require attention \u2014 expect to invest in repairs to get it running reliably. This listing is best suited for a mechanically inclined buyer, someone looking for a project vehicle, or a buyer who needs basic transportation and is prepared for the car's shortcomings. There are no hidden surprises here \u2014 what you see is what you get, and the price reflects the car's true state.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and represents a solid, dependable used car purchase. The exterior presents well with only minor surface blemishes \u2014 light scuffs and small scratches consistent with normal use \u2014 but no significant dents or paint damage. The body panels are straight and the paint retains a reasonable shine. The interior is clean and well-maintained, with seats showing modest wear but no tears or major staining. All primary controls, windows, and climate systems function properly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and reliably, with no warning lights or known mechanical issues. The tires have good tread remaining and the brakes are in serviceable condition. This is not a showroom-perfect vehicle, but it is genuinely road-ready and well cared for \u2014 a buyer can expect a comfortable, trouble-free driving experience without the premium price of a near-mint example.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition at $18,000, and that's a straightforward, honest assessment. The exterior shows clear signs of use \u2014 you can expect noticeable scratches, areas of paint fading, and possibly a small dent or two. The interior reflects similar wear, with some scuffs on surfaces and likely some fading on the upholstery. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but given its condition, a pre-purchase inspection is strongly recommended to identify any items that may need attention in the near term. This is a practical, budget-conscious option for a buyer who understands they're getting a well-used vehicle and is comfortable with some ongoing maintenance. No major surprises are being hidden here \u2014 what you see is what you get.",
      "price": 18000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    }
